Hugh Buckler https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugh_Buckler 0 Hugh Buckler (September 9, 1881 – October 30, 1936) was a British actor. He was the father of the actor John Buckler, with whom he was in a fatal road accident in 1936. Hugh_Buckler ( September_9_,_1881 – October_30_,_1936 ) was a_British_actor .
